author: doll
msg: The first part of a very very simple implementation of a sever side backed opensocial container. This involves creating the opensocial-0.7 feature with a json based container which talks back to a servlet at /socialdata.
This code is littered with todos and needs tons of fleshing out. However, it does successfully render the SocialHelloWorld gadget and gets us started down the path of supporting opensocial for real.
